data.meta_description: View the profile of Justin Thane
data.text: Hello, my name is Justin Thane and I specialize in commercial real estate in the Southern Suburbs of Cape Town. I have a passion for the industry and find it to be challenging, competitive and rewarding. I have a corporate background, having worked in the banking industry for 10 years in London. My top reason to work with me is that I have a passion for property, I'm open, honest, and reliable. I strive to find the best suited property for my client's needs. I am confident that I can help you achieve your commercial real estate goals.
